{"tid":2175586,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律師指許智峯不適送院　又稱警拒許智峯申請保釋","createTime":"2020-08-26T14:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T14:31:38.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4409eb8b067f85cbbfd8c8876432f572f7c32591","tid":2175586,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:22:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546052-20200826.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546052-20200826.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhatgaB4GmEhO8grhZepf4200Y%3D&h=1c41f33c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546052-20200826.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=45ee8c91\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546052-20200826.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員許智峯的社交專頁，引述代表律師指許智峯因突然身體不適，送往北區醫院，又表示許智峯下午1時半已完成所有調查程序，但警方一直拒絕讓許智峯申請保釋，亦拒絕交代情況。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯透過律師表示，他當日只是履行議員職責，調停糾紛，反被警方指控，形容是警方濫捕濫告、顛倒黑白的例子，亦反映政府繼續以政治檢控，打壓港人爭取公義及行使公民權利。他表示，不會因而懼怕強權打壓，會繼續爭取公義，包括監察警方濫暴行為，並以私人檢控追究警暴。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯今早6時於寓所被捕，指他去年7月6日於屯門示威現場涉嫌妨礙司法公正、有犯罪及不誠實意圖取用電腦及刑事毀壞。"},{"pid":"3faf742826513064ba4d1d4e984d5531686ffc01","tid":2175586,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5781baae2276c1b65cb4c18eb4c4a6c1d3d3928a","tid":2175586,"uid":23085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:29:11.000Z","msg":"明顯係報服佢告狗"},{"pid":"9e3819ed6b2e0f9c366fe26aec1cdb85d0695cfd","tid":2175586,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"係醫院訓夠48直接做佢"},{"pid":"c2d0cfaad64e1bdeeb82db21fce870ef5253142b","tid":2175586,"uid":287751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:30:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">借個位<br />\n831 有行動</span><br 